{"parentUuid":"0c081b69-be95-411b-886b-707d3094050d","isSidechain":false,"attachment":{"type":"task_reminder","content":[{"id":"1","subject":"Rename --force semantics and add real blind --force","description":"Issue #47. Today's --force is lease-protected (sends captured Old). Rename it to --force-with-lease. Add a new --force that is the real git push --force (Old=ZeroHash on non-deletes, no lease).\n\nSurface to change:\n- cmd/git-sync/syncplan.go:112 — flag definition\n- cmd/git-sync-bench/main.go:109 — bench flag\n- types.go SyncPolicy.Force — rename to ForceWithLease, add new Force\n- client.go:233, internalbridge/config.go:87, unstable/client.go:267 — plumbing\n- internal/syncer/syncer.go — cfg.Force, cfg.ForceWithLease wiring; reject both at once\n- internal/planner/planner.go:179, planner.go:305 — planner accepts non-FF if either flag set\n- internal/convert/convert.go:62 — when blind force is on, send Old=ZeroHash for non-delete commands\n- bootstrap/replicate guards at syncer.go:930, :563 — reject both flags\n- docs/usage.md and CHANGELOG.md unreleased","activeForm":"Renaming --force and adding blind --force","status":"in_progress","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"2","subject":"Document lease behavior in docs/usage.md","description":"Add a short section explaining: target ref state is captured at session start; the captured value is sent as Old on every push command, so receive-pack rejects updates where the target moved during the run. This is `--force-with-lease` semantics. The new `--force` opts out.","activeForm":"Documenting lease behavior","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"3","subject":"Hint on lease-failure ng status","description":"When a non-BestEffort run hits a receive-pack ng with the \"stale info / does not match expected old value\" pattern, augment the error with: \"target ref moved during sync; rerun, or use --force (without --force-with-lease) to overwrite.\" Lives in the rejection-handling path in internal/gitproto/push.go and/or its callers.","activeForm":"Adding lease-failure hint","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]}],"itemCount":3},"type":"attachment","uuid":"cfb3c933-cdc3-446a-bf48-d2cd2b0c29c1","timestamp":"2026-05-12T21:19:37.514Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/git-sync","sessionId":"aefcb05b-206d-434a-94bf-d11991a74a0a","version":"2.1.129","gitBranch":"main"}
